data.description: Welcome to this standout 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home located in the sought-after Arbutus area of Halethorpe. Set on a spacious corner lot, this residence showcases hardwood flooring on the main level, complemented by modern stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. An expansive unfinished basement offers potential for personal customization.  The property's exterior boasts a vast backyard, ideal for outdoor activities, as well as wide front stairs leading up to a large welcoming porch, setting the tone for the home's inviting ambiance.  Conveniently situated minutes from major highways 695 and 95, local shopping hubs, the MARC train station, and the scenic Patapsco State Park, this property seamlessly blends prime location with top-tier features.
